{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "motus-debug-api-collection",
    "name": "MOTUS Debug API",
    "description": "Debug API for UKG-to-Motus data synchronization validation.\n\nThis collection provides endpoints to:\n- Fetch raw data from UKG (via Debug API or Direct)\n- Build Motus driver payloads\n- Compare UKG data with Motus current state\n- Validate specific scenarios (new hire, termination, etc.)\n- Sync employees to Motus\n- Direct UKG API calls with authentication\n- Direct Motus API calls with authentication\n\n**Environment Variables Required:**\n- `base_url`: Debug API base URL (default: http://localhost:8000)\n- `company_id`: UKG Company ID (default: J9A6Y)\n- `UKG_BASE_URL`: UKG API base URL\n- `UKG_BASIC_B64`: Base64 encoded username:password for UKG\n- `UKG_CUSTOMER_API_KEY`: UKG customer API key\n- `MOTUS_API_BASE`: Motus API base URL\n- `MOTUS_JWT`: Motus Bearer JWT token\n\n**Test EEIDs:**\n- New Hire: 28190, 28203, 28207, 28209, 28210\n- Termination: 26737, 27991, 28069, 23497, 27938\n- Manager Change: 28195\n- Address Change: 25336, 26421, 10858, 22299\n- Leave: 022393, 028027, 026434",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Check API health status."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Direct UKG API",
      "description": "Direct calls to UKG Pro API endpoints.\n\n**Authentication Required:**\n- Basic Auth: Base64(username:password) in Authorization header\n- US-CUSTOMER-API-KEY: Customer API key header\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set UKG_BASE_URL (e.g., https://service5.ultipro.com)\n2. Set UKG_BASIC_B64 = Base64 encode of 'username:password'\n3. Set UKG_CUSTOMER_API_KEY = your API key",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Employment Details",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Basic {{UKG_BASIC_B64}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "US-CUSTOMER-API-KEY",
                "value": "{{UKG_CUSTOMER_API_KEY}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UKG_BASE_URL}}/personnel/v1/employment-details?employeeNumber={{employee_number}}&companyIds={{company_id}}",
              "host": ["{{UKG_BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["personnel", "v1", "employment-details"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "employeeNumber",
                  "value": "{{employee_number}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "companyIds",
                  "value": "{{company_id}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get employment details directly from UKG Pro API.\n\nReturns employee employment information including:\n- primaryJobCode\n- employeeStatusCode\n- hireDate\n- terminationDate\n- fullTimeOrPartTimeCode\n- homeLocationCode\n- supervisorId"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Person Details",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Basic {{UKG_BASIC_B64}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "US-CUSTOMER-API-KEY",
                "value": "{{UKG_CUSTOMER_API_KEY}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UKG_BASE_URL}}/personnel/v1/person-details/{{employee_id}}",
              "host": ["{{UKG_BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["personnel", "v1", "person-details", "{{employee_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Get person details directly from UKG Pro API.\n\nRequires employee_id (not employee_number).\n\nReturns personal information including:\n- firstName, lastName, middleName\n- address (line1, city, state, postalCode, country)\n- emailAddress\n- mobilePhone\n- homePhone"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Supervisor Details",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Basic {{UKG_BASIC_B64}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "US-CUSTOMER-API-KEY",
                "value": "{{UKG_CUSTOMER_API_KEY}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UKG_BASE_URL}}/personnel/v1/supervisor-details/{{employee_id}}",
              "host": ["{{UKG_BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["personnel", "v1", "supervisor-details", "{{employee_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Get supervisor details directly from UKG Pro API.\n\nRequires employee_id (not employee_number).\n\nReturns supervisor information including:\n- supervisorFirstName\n- supervisorLastName"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Locations",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Basic {{UKG_BASIC_B64}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "US-CUSTOMER-API-KEY",
                "value": "{{UKG_CUSTOMER_API_KEY}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UKG_BASE_URL}}/configuration/v1/org-levels",
              "host": ["{{UKG_BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["configuration", "v1", "org-levels"]
            },
            "description": "Get organization levels/locations from UKG Pro API.\n\nReturns location information used for:\n- Mapping homeLocationCode to location name\n- Division hierarchy"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get All Employees (Batch)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Basic {{UKG_BASIC_B64}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "US-CUSTOMER-API-KEY",
                "value": "{{UKG_CUSTOMER_API_KEY}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UKG_BASE_URL}}/personnel/v1/employment-details?companyIds={{company_id}}&per_page=100&page=1",
              "host": ["{{UKG_BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["personnel", "v1", "employment-details"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "companyIds",
                  "value": "{{company_id}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "per_page",
                  "value": "100"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get all employment details for batch processing.\n\nPagination:\n- per_page: Number of records per page (default 100)\n- page: Page number (starts at 1)\n\nUsed for batch sync operations."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Direct Motus API",
      "description": "Direct calls to Motus API endpoints.\n\n**Authentication Required:**\n- Bearer JWT token in Authorization header\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set MOTUS_API_BASE (e.g., https://api.motus.com/v1)\n2. Set MOTUS_JWT = JWT token from motus-get-token.py",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Driver",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{MOTUS_JWT}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{MOTUS_API_BASE}}/drivers/{{employee_number}}",
              "host": ["{{MOTUS_API_BASE}}"],
              "path": ["drivers", "{{employee_number}}"]
            },
            "description": "Get driver details directly from Motus API.\n\nUses clientEmployeeId1 (employee_number) to lookup driver.\n\nReturns:\n- Driver profile information\n- Custom variables (Manager Name, Division, etc.)\n- Program assignment\n- Status (Active, Terminated, etc.)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Driver (POST)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{MOTUS_JWT}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"clientEmployeeId1\": \"{{employee_number}}\",\n  \"programId\": 21232,\n  \"firstName\": \"Test\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Driver\",\n  \"email\": \"test.driver@example.com\",\n  \"address1\": \"123 Main St\",\n  \"city\": \"Anytown\",\n  \"state\": \"CA\",\n  \"postalCode\": \"90210\",\n  \"country\": \"US\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2024-01-01\",\n  \"phone\": \"555-1234\",\n  \"customVariables\": {\n    \"Manager Name\": \"John Manager\",\n    \"Division\": \"Sales\",\n    \"Division Number\": \"001\",\n    \"UKG Id\": \"{{employee_number}}\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{MOTUS_API_BASE}}/drivers",
              "host": ["{{MOTUS_API_BASE}}"],
              "path": ["drivers"]
            },
            "description": "Create a new driver in Motus.\n\n**Required Fields:**\n- clientEmployeeId1 (employee number)\n- programId (21232=FAVR, 21233=CPM)\n- firstName, lastName, email\n- address1, city, state, postalCode, country\n- startDate (YYYY-MM-DD)\n\n**Optional Fields:**\n- phone\n- customVariables (Manager Name, Division, etc.)\n\n**WARNING**: This creates a real driver in Motus!"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Driver (PUT)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{MOTUS_JWT}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"clientEmployeeId1\": \"{{employee_number}}\",\n  \"programId\": 21232,\n  \"firstName\": \"Test\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Driver\",\n  \"email\": \"test.driver@example.com\",\n  \"address1\": \"456 New Address\",\n  \"city\": \"Newtown\",\n  \"state\": \"NY\",\n  \"postalCode\": \"10001\",\n  \"country\": \"US\",\n  \"phone\": \"555-5678\",\n  \"customVariables\": {\n    \"Manager Name\": \"Jane Manager\",\n    \"Division\": \"Marketing\",\n    \"Division Number\": \"002\",\n    \"UKG Id\": \"{{employee_number}}\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{MOTUS_API_BASE}}/drivers/{{employee_number}}",
              "host": ["{{MOTUS_API_BASE}}"],
              "path": ["drivers", "{{employee_number}}"]
            },
            "description": "Update an existing driver in Motus.\n\n**Note:** Do NOT include startDate for updates - it cannot be modified.\n\n**Fields that can be updated:**\n- firstName, lastName, email\n- address1, city, state, postalCode, country\n- phone\n- customVariables\n- endDate (for terminations)\n\n**WARNING**: This makes real changes to Motus!"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Terminate Driver",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{MOTUS_JWT}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"clientEmployeeId1\": \"{{employee_number}}\",\n  \"programId\": 21232,\n  \"endDate\": \"2024-12-31\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{MOTUS_API_BASE}}/drivers/{{employee_number}}",
              "host": ["{{MOTUS_API_BASE}}"],
              "path": ["drivers", "{{employee_number}}"]
            },
            "description": "Terminate a driver by setting their endDate.\n\n**Fields:**\n- endDate: Termination date in YYYY-MM-DD format\n\nOnce endDate is set, driver status becomes 'Terminated'.\n\n**WARNING**: This makes real changes to Motus!"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
